  "body": "Steps to reproduce: \r\n- run TG and RPCDaemon\r\n- run `echo \"POST http://localhost:8545 \\n Content-Type: application/json \\n @$(pwd)/cmd/rpctest/getLogs.json\" | vegeta attack -rate=300 -duration=100s -timeout=1000s | vegeta report`\r\n- RpcDaemon will serve requests well\r\n- Shutdown TG\r\n- RPCDaemon will show in logs: \r\n```\r\nWARN [10-20|14:23:20.457] Served                                   conn=127.0.0.1:63559 method=eth_getLogs reqid=537758 t=\"983.258Âµs\" err=\"getting latest block number: rpc error: code = Unimplemented desc = unknown service remote.KV2\"\r\nWARN [10-20|14:23:20.461] received unexpected error from server after CloseSend err=\"rpc error: code = Unimplemented desc = unknown service remote.KV2\"\r\n```\r\n- Start TG \r\n- RPCDaemon will still show same logs, but it must re-connect and serve new requests successfully\r\n- Please review also code around `CloseSend` method - because as I understand we must see errors earlier (not when closing cursor, probably need hide this error). \r\n",
